
## Dependency Network

Here's an overview of of the packages **`r reporter$pkg_name`** relies upon.

### Visualization

```{r pressure, echo=FALSE}
result <- tryCatch({
    reporter$graph_viz
}, error = function(e){
    return(sprintf("DependencyReporter failed with error -->     %s", e$message))
})
result
```

### Table

```{r}
result <- tryCatch({
    reporter$get_summary_view()
}, error = function(e){
    return(sprintf("DependencyReporter failed with error %s", e$message))
})
```
